	"data": "<div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَهُوَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٱلَّذِي يَتَوَفَّىٰكُم بِٱلَّيۡلِ وَيَعۡلَمُ مَا <a data-content='كسبتم فيه بجوارحكم من الإثم' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>جَرَحۡتُم بِٱلنَّهَارِ</a> </div><div>ثُمَّ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>يَبۡعَثُكُمۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> فِيهِ لِيُقۡضَىٰٓ أَجَلٞ مُّسَمّٗىۖ ثُمَّ إِلَيۡهِ مَرۡجِعُكُمۡ </div><div>ثُمَّ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>يُنَبِّئُكُم</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> بِمَا كُنتُمۡ تَعۡمَلُونَ ٦٠ وَهُوَ ٱلۡقَاهِرُ فَوۡقَ </div><div>عِبَادِهِۦۖ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَيُرۡسِلُ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> عَلَيۡكُمۡ حَفَظَةً حَتَّىٰٓ إِذَا جَآءَ أَحَدَكُمُ ٱلۡمَوۡتُ </div><div>تَوَفَّتۡهُ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>رُسُلُنَا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَهُمۡ <a data-content='لا يتوانون أو لا يُقصّرون' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>لَا يُفَرِّطُونَ</a> ٦١ ثُمَّ رُدُّوٓاْ إِلَى ٱللَّهِ مَوۡلَىٰهُمُ </div><div>ٱلۡحَقِّۚ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>أَلَا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> لَهُ ٱلۡحُكۡمُ وَهُوَ أَسۡرَعُ ٱلۡحَٰسِبِينَ ٦٢ قُلۡ مَن يُنَجِّيكُم </div><div>مِّن</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ظُلُمَٰتِ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٱلۡبَرِّ وَٱلۡبَحۡرِ تَدۡعُونَهُۥ <a data-content='مُعلنين الضّراعة والتذلّل له' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>تَضَرُّعٗا</a> <a data-content='مسرّين بالدّعاء' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>وَخُفۡيَةٗ</a> لَّئِنۡ أَنجَىٰنَا </div><div>مِنۡ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.3vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>هَٰذِهِۦ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> لَنَكُونَنَّ مِنَ ٱلشَّٰكِرِينَ ٦٣ قُلِ ٱللَّهُ يُنَجِّيكُم مِّنۡهَا وَمِن كُلِّ </div><div>كَرۡبٖ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.6vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ثُمَّ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> أَنتُمۡ تُشۡرِكُونَ ٦٤ قُلۡ هُوَ ٱلۡقَادِرُ عَلَىٰٓ أَن يَبۡعَثَ عَلَيۡكُمۡ عَذَابٗا </div><div>مِّن</div></div><div style='font-size:4.6vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>فَوۡقِكُمۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> أَوۡ مِن تَحۡتِ أَرۡجُلِكُمۡ أَوۡ <a data-content='يخلطكم في ملاحم القتال' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>يَلۡبِسَكُمۡ</a> <a data-content='فِرقا مُختلفة الأهواء' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>شِيَعٗا</a> وَيُذِيقَ </div><div>بَعۡضَكُم</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div><a data-content='شدّة بعض في القتال' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>بَأۡسَ بَعۡضٍۗ</a> ٱنظُرۡ كَيۡفَ </div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'><a data-content='نكرّرها بأساليب مختلفة' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>نُصَرِّفُ ٱلۡأٓيَٰتِ</a> لَعَلَّهُمۡ يَفۡقَهُونَ ٦٥ </div><div>وَكَذَّبَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>بِهِۦ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> قَوۡمُكَ وَهُوَ ٱلۡحَقُّۚ قُل لَّسۡتُ عَلَيۡكُم <a data-content='بحفيظ وكّل إليّ أمركم فأجازيكم' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>بِوَكِيلٖ</a> ٦٦ لِّكُلِّ </div><div>نَبَإٖ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>مُّسۡتَقَرّٞۚ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَسَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ ٦٧ وَإِذَا رَأَيۡتَ ٱلَّذِينَ <a data-content='يأخذون في الاستهزاء والطّعن' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>يَخُوضُونَ</a> فِيٓ </div><div>ءَايَٰتِنَا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>فَأَعۡرِضۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> عَنۡهُمۡ حَتَّىٰ يَخُوضُواْ فِي حَدِيثٍ غَيۡرِهِۦۚ وَإِمَّا </div><div>يُنسِيَنَّكَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱلشَّيۡطَٰنُ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> فَلَا تَقۡعُدۡ بَعۡدَ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰ مَعَ ٱلۡقَوۡمِ ٱلظَّٰلِمِينَ </div><div>٦٨</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'></div>",
